											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The Flaming Fists look up to see the the dragon flying right towards them. They turn to run but the dragon is too fast for them. As he flies over the flaming fists the dragon breathes fire and burns them to death. The bridge also catches fire during the attack and is destroyed. Finally, the dragon lands by the foot of the bridge and its rider Kith'rak Voss, dismounts and joins the other Githyanki warriors." />
